sequenceDiagram

    actor Dev as Developer
    participant Agent as Agent<br/>(reasoning loop)
    participant Tools as Tool Layer<br/>(scoped, sandboxed)
    participant System as System Under<br/>Modification
    participant Trace as Observability<br/>Trace

    Note over Dev,Trace: Task Definition Phase

    Dev->>Agent: Define task + context<br/>(desired outcome, constraints)
    Agent->>Trace: Log task + initial reasoning

    Note over Dev,Trace: Planning Phase

    Agent->>Agent: Generate plan<br/>(steps + tool calls)
    Agent->>Dev: Present plan for review
    Agent->>Trace: Log plan

    alt Plan needs revision
        Dev->>Agent: Modify plan / add constraints
        Agent->>Agent: Revise plan
    else Plan approved
        Dev->>Agent: Approve plan
    end

    Note over Dev,Trace: Execution Phase &mdash; routine actions

    loop For each routine step
        Agent->>Tools: Tool call (read, list, query)
        Tools->>System: Execute (sandboxed, scoped)
        System-->>Tools: Result
        Tools-->>Agent: Tool result
        Agent->>Trace: Log call + parameters + result
    end

    Note over Dev,Trace: Human-in-the-Loop Checkpoint

    Agent->>Dev: High-stakes action requires approval<br/>(deploy / delete / write)
    Dev->>Agent: Approve / reject / modify
    Agent->>Trace: Log decision + reasoning

    alt Approved
        Agent->>Tools: Execute high-stakes action
        Tools->>System: Apply change
        System-->>Tools: Result
        Tools-->>Agent: Confirmation
    else Rejected
        Agent->>Agent: Adjust plan or halt
    end

    Note over Dev,Trace: Verification Phase

    Agent->>Tools: Verify outcome<br/>(re-read state, check signals)
    Tools->>System: Read for verification
    System-->>Tools: Current state
    Tools-->>Agent: Verification result
    Agent->>Trace: Log verification

    alt Verification passed
        Agent->>Dev: Task complete + summary
    else Verification failed
        Agent->>Dev: Failure + diagnostic + suggested next step
    end

    Note over Dev,Trace: Trace queryable post-hoc<br/>by run ID for debugging
